          "reviewBody": "Schiller is one of the best schools in Ghaziabad. All the teachers here are very supportive and encouraging. The best part is following a curriculum with a perfect blend of modern education and culture. Hope for same in future.\nNeeraj and Shikha Garg( Parents of Sanchi Garg)",
          "publisher": {
