          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is a very old school as compared to the new schools being established these days .\nAs being old it has good management system.. which helps in bringing out nice product (students in life)\nApart from this even if it is very old but still they have not increased their number of sections in one class which inturn results in more concentration on each and every student of the school.\nTherefore it helps in holistic development of the student. As my child is in class kg .\nThe teachers of pre primary wing are very energetic helpful lively and every quality which a student needs in his teacher are present.\nOverall a good choice of school if seeing for pre primary child",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
