            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Love this school, my kid love to be there with his supportive, loving teachers and friends. Teachers always try to encourage and make the most from the kids input. They not only focus on studies also try to improve their over all motor skills.",
          "publisher": {
