            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the finest school in Ghaziabad. Trainings and exposure provided for individual. Management is cooperative. Staff are all good and helping. School's policies are fair and management's vision and expectations are clear. Management has created an evironment that low on work place politics and full on professional energy. The team is highly experienced and dedicated. I love to work at this school. My experience is moreover good. I enjoy teaching here and also enhance my knowledge.\n\nLast but not the least...overall...it is a good school where you can enjoy teaching. :)\n\nRegards,\nAkriti Chaudhary.",
